Strategy_resp: I imagined myself sitting in a restaurant, and thought of the things I'd expect to see while I'm there.
I tried to picture all the animals I imagine on farms, in the ocean, and inside zoos.
I tried to remember the last time I was in a hotel and I tried to remember the things I remembered seeing while I was there.
I just thought of the letter 'F'with different letters as the second letter, and tried to think of words by doing that.
I just thought of the letter 's' with various letters as the second letter after it, to try to think up words easily.
I tried to think of all the sports that I remember from High School and sports I remembered seeing in The Olympics
I just tried to think of all the letters that could come after the letter 'a' then figured out words from there
I just tried really hard to think of the different professions that I've ever seen on Tv or in real life
I just tried to think of things I remembered being kept in my parents' garage and my friends parents' garages, as well as things I keep in my own garage.
